Interface JQ.DeferredHandler<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - Type of the value carried by the promise to be observed by clients
    Enclosing class:
    JQ

    public static interface JQ.DeferredHandler<V>
    Callback interface used by deferrer to get access to the Deferred object

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void handle(JQ.Deferred<V> deferred)
      Callback implemented by the deferrer to get access to the Deferred object.

    • Method Detail

      • handle

        void handle(JQ.Deferred<V> deferred)
        Callback implemented by the deferrer to get access to the Deferred object. Caller should carry out the deferred task and upon completion call JQ.Deferred.resolve(Object) or JQ.Deferred.reject(Exception), respectively.
        Parameters:
        deferred - Deferred object carrying the promise to be observed by clients
